						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/Commodities/Livestock/Related-developments/Ghana-Turning-cassava-peel-into-animal-feed" title="Ghana: Turning cassava peel into animal feed" alt="link">Ghana: Turning cassava peel into animal feed</a></h2>

	
					<p>Students from the Kwadaso Agricultural College in Ghana have set up a company to recycle waste cassava peels into animal feed that has the potential to replace maize.<a href="http://www.allaboutfeed.net/Processing/General/2013/4/Ghana-Turning-cassava-peel-into-animal-feed-1229478W/" target="_self">http://www.allaboutfeed.net/Processing/General/2013/4/Ghana-Turning-cassava-peel-into-animal-feed-1229478W/</a>(All About Feed, 15/04/2013)</p>
							<p><span class="date">22/05/2013</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/Commodities/Livestock/Related-developments/Ghana-Turning-cassava-peel-into-animal-feed">Read more...</a>
